data.description: Absolute stunning three bedrooms with an office plus a bonus room, two bath, pool home nesting on a fully fenced acre. Immerse yourself in the tranquility of this exquisite residence nestled in the charming community of Barrington Oaks. This stunning property boasts a seamless blend of modern luxury and timeless elegance, offering an unparalleled living experience in the heart of Dover, Florida. Why wait for new construction when you have this updated home that is move in ready? This quiet community is about .5 of a mile to I4 making your Tampa or Orlando trips a breeze. Take advantage of the upgraded solar panels. You'll be welcome with new tile throughout with new carpet in the bedrooms, new paint and fixtures throughout, both bathroom offer amazing new touches including vanity, tub, faucets and paint. New roof (2023), AC (2022) and new fans in the interior and back patio. Stop by and take the tour of your next home.
